        <h5>Introduction to Responsive Design:</h5>
        <p class="mt-3">Responsive design in Canvas app Power Apps refers to the practice of creating an application interface that dynamically adjusts and adapts its layout and components based on the screen size and orientation of the device on which it is being viewed.</p>
        <p class="mt-3">Key principles of responsive design in Canvas apps include:</p>
        <ol class="d-flex flex-column pb-3 justify-content-center gap-2">
            <li>Flexible Layouts: Designing layouts that can fluidly expand, contract, or reorganize based on available screen space.</li>
        </ol>
